OL,7,FThe Northern Ireland Troubles (Legacy
OL,8,Fand Reconciliation) Act 2023 faced
OL,9,Fopposition throughout its passage
OL,10,Fthrough Parliament from political
OL,11,Fparties, victim's organisations and
OL,12,Fthe Irish Government.
OL,14,FDespite this, the Legay Act received
OL,15,Froyal assent in September.
OL,17,FSeparately, the Irish Government has
OL,18,Flaunched an interstate legal case
OL,19,Fagainst the UK Government over the
OL,20,FLegacy Act, arguing that it breaches
OL,21,Fhuman rights laws.
