OL,7,FSome political figures in Nrothern
OL,8,FIreland have called on the Government
OL,9,Fto suspend the Act following the High
OL,10,FCourt ruling.
OL,12,FAlliance Party deputy leader Stephen
OL,13,FFarry said it was no surprise that the
OL,14,FAct had been "unpicked at its first
OL,15,Flegal challenge".
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland Secretary of State
OL,18,FChris Heaton-Harris said that the
OL,19,Fgovernment "remain committed to
OL,20,Fimplementing the Legacy Act."
