OL,7,FThe Secretary was questioned in the
OL,8,FCommons by Shadow Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fsecretary Hilary Benn said immunity
OL,10,Ffrom prosecution had been a central
OL,11,Ffoundation of the Legacy Act.
OL,13,FHe added: "What do ministers intend to
OL,14,Fdo about this judgment and how can the
OL,15,FCommission (ICRIR) become operational
OL,16,Fwhen one of its central powers has
OL,17,Fjust been struck down?"
